snippet.textDisplay: This song is so heartfelt ❤ while listening to this almost everyday i wonder can we ever heal from all the wounds we get in the process of loving someone? It gets heavy day by day turning our heart into void.  Why being in love is painful when it should be otherwise? I remember playing this song to the love of my life when i found out he was never mine, and all the tears flowing due to the heart-wrenching lyrics this song has, every line made sense and could feel it to the soul. Guess we would never know why we get weak in the name of love. Cheers to all the hearts who was in love but couldn't get the reciprocated love they deserved!
